name: Vishal V

sonaquiz.summary: Recent activities in the sonaquiz repository have focused on significant enhancements to the quiz system, including the addition of end time handling, department report functionality, and email functionality using Nodemailer. The repository has also seen improvements to the user management system, including the implementation of user analytics, deletion functionality, and role-based access control. Additionally, various bug fixes and UI enhancements have been made to the dashboard and history components, including the implementation of CSV export functionality for user analytics and quiz scores.
